    @template mod_learningmap/backtomap

    Template for displaying the "back to learning map" button in activity descriptions.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * none

    Example context (json):
    {
    "url": "https://moodle.localhost/mod/learningmap/view.php?id=1234",
    "name": "Learningmap"
    }
}}
<div class="learningmap-backlink">
    <a href="{{{url}}}" class="learningmap-icon">{{#str}} backlink, learningmap, { "name": {{#quote}}{{name}}{{/quote}} } {{/str}}</a>
</div>